    "question_id" : 79816681,
    "body" : "<p>I think you've created a red herring for yourself by calling the output you want &quot;random&quot;.  One of your criteria is that the computation be deterministic -- always the same output for the same input -- so it's not random at all.  You <em>can</em> nevertheless use a pseudorandom number generator to do the job by manipulating its seed, but that seems a bit overkill.</p>\n",
